title: Head Moderator and Moderator Team Compensation
body:
The team currently consists of 1 Head Mod and 8 Mods total. Please note the amount voted upon will be split amongst the mods on a Bi-Weekly basis. (every other week)

Total Bi-Weekly Compensation:
- 1 Eth     (.1e/mod + .2e/headmod)
- 1.5 Eth  (.15e/mod + .3e/headmod)
- 2 Eth    (.2e/mod + .4e/headmod)
- 2.5 Eth (.25e/mod + .5e/headmod)
- 3 Eth    (.3e/mod + .6e/headmod)
- 3.5 Eth (.35e/mod + .7e/headmod)
- 4 Eth    (.4e/mod + .8e/headmod)
